1bcddd5513","tid":1009915,"uid":150347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"我真係唔了解啦，買番黎既仲多過自己生產既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904f8036aa0c71a6110f683c983b32f18c54561b","tid":1009915,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T00:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔清楚，但依d演習係咪有空空對抗？模擬dog fight?<br />\n<br />\n咁唔派j20都正常，部機本身都可能多破綻，比戰機雷達keep住掃，到真打比人無限放大就唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國應該都唔敢派F22同非盟國演習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 機密野愈少人知愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}